Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.79,0:01:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Our story begins in a land far away, in a time known to none, in a place known to none.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There once was a young king who ruled the kingdom of Heinrogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.75,0:01:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes there!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive my rudeness, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the knight captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Captain Jenatos, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.90,0:01:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you think me an enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the spirits of the night visit the ramparts at this hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,let alone the king himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for startling you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.49,0:02:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You did nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.33,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenatos, please tell me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is spring so late to come this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It is strange... It's been far more cold than normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,May is supposed to begin tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I suppose it is the end of April.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The fields are still white with frost, keeping the plants from budding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.64,0:02:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The world should be bathed in the color of vibrant flowers, but not one is to be seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes that's just how nature is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good has happened since my father died and I took the throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... You're worrying too much, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Famine. Plague. War. Am I just too weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the kingdom doomed to suffer at the hands of a novice king in their twenties?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.19,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, your highness!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The country needs its king the most when times are tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.07,0:03:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What could I even do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm powerless to help the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.12,0:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.21,0:03:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I had knowledge...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ravens again... They've been increasing, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.83,0:03:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably... since there's been more deaths lately...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:04:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten... Twenty... Where are they headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably to the barren mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...you said you desired power, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I suppose I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What must a monarch have to turn an ashen country into a prosperous one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've said, the king's abilities affect the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That is not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Every man needs a source of power. A king is no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Powerful kings of yore had powerful benefactors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Benefactors?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:05:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know of the stone ruins on top of that barren mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, the temple that once laid there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.04,0:05:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When night comes again, head there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wishes will surely be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, Jenatos!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to find out on your own. Now if you'll excuse me, I need to patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.02,0:05:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to read tomorrow's schedule, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In the morning, an ambassador from our neighbor wishes to meet with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.57,0:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like a private reception room? Or in the public hall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Private room, it is. Next, the mayor of Rune Malna wishes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.20,0:05:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening, your highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening. What does he want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.74,0:05:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be about the worsening food supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like my words will fix anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.77,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,After lunch, you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But, your highness—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the schedule there. I'll make sure to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.95,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Good night then, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Marina...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem dreadfully tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.90,0:06:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.62,0:06:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get to bed right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.12,0:06:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's somewhere I have to go tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,At this hour? Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back before you know it. Please don't wait up for me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an important time to take care of your body, so please rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.03,0:07:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.99,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, my lady. Is the king not coming to bed yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no... Something seems to have come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let's lower your hair and get you ready for bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.68,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so jealous of your beautiful long, blonde hair~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Your chestnut-brown hair is lovely too, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But wow, the king is really cool yet gentle, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...I hope Lewis comes back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this light?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening! Where you off to at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fara! And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,King Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.67,0:08:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! You're a human king!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, but wasn't the king, uh, Rudolph or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my great-grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.91,0:08:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, I forget that humans don't live all that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fairy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pixie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Pixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lewis, this might be rude of me, but you shouldn't go any further this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems a bunch of monsters are gathering on the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm off! In a bit of a hurry myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What was I in a hurry for again...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...? Why did Jenatos tell me to come to a gathering of ghouls and goblins...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.76,0:09:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept us waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Our special guest has arrived, but he seems to be hiding! Hehehehe...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There! You must be Heinrogue's king, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.57,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.02,0:09:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the first I've seen. You wish for power, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking if you wish for power, riches, and wisdom!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:09:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall make you the richest, wisest, and most powerful of kings. Now, stick out your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.07,0:10:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All you must do is accept this ring, and your wishes shall be granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.36,0:10:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Um—\N-Now, put on the ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what, are you afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. Now, your dreams will now become your reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In return... Once the time is right, your most precious thing will become mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hahahahahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just entered a blood pact with me, Gizafeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.18,0:11:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,HAHAHAHAHA!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,AHHHH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A few months passed since then. As promised, King Lewis's luck turned around,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and the country seemed on the road to recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.70,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You called for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, minister! I've been waiting. I seek your counsel about our current lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.38,0:12:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this map. If we wish to extend the highway to Nautilus, we'll have to cut through the Pixian Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.75,0:12:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,While we're there, why don't we just clear the whole forest and turn it into farmland?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But sir, that's there the pixies and elves live—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.38,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What can we do? A prosperous nation needs a powerful economy and military.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can have all of that with this highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.65,0:12:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,How much manpower would this take, minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.45,0:12:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My liege, I'm sure you're very much aware,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but the people are exhausted from repeated war and hardships. Any more would be—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the nation! If it falls, the people fall with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.68,0:12:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't my policies led to our victory at war and the rapid growth of our economy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I'm wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your happiness does not equal the people's happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please think of those who lost loved ones to war, or those struggling under heavy taxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't my people just that? MY people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.58,0:13:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness! Please refrain from speaking like that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,-You'll turn the people against—\N-That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.49,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a waste of time talking to my foolish minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rethink this.\N-Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.70,0:13:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, it's time to prepare for the banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Another banquet... Luxurious banquets nearly every night can't possibly be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,These beautiful clothes and delicacies are being paid for by the people's taxes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The king will be upset if you don't show up in your finest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Lewis has really changed... This jewel he gave me was something plundered from our neighboring country!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel the blood on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, try not to see only the bad in everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me open the window so we can relax with some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.90,0:14:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? A pixie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, my name's Fara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest where we all live is being chopped down. Please, do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.64,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? The Pixian Forest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Another section was just leveled today!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The king's just said progress is going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroying the forest is "progress"!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try talking with the king. Though, I don't know if he'll listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The lush forests don't belong to just one group!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even humans will fall to ruin if they keep cutting down the trees! Make sure the king knows that!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenatos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Gizafeal...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rejoice, for the fruit has ripened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.06,0:15:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired of standing watch on these cold walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.67,0:15:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the knight captain, yet you're treated like dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the royal family sleeps warm and cozy in the luxury of the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:16:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it not the soldiers who won the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A... a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're currently indulging in the finest of liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, the people will rally behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill King Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then become the king yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear, I wish to ask you about the Pixian Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh, the forest we're building the highway through. With that road built, access to the harbor will be much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.93,0:16:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just the road either! With all that lumber, we can craft ships and use the cleared land for crops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we should build a workshop there too to make weapons, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, reconsider this plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the home of the pixies and the elves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That forest... No, all the forests, mountains, and rivers all belong to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.05,0:17:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I wonder if the pixies or the elves could be put to work for the benefit of the country...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.65,0:17:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave all the political matters to me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just relax and enjoy being adorned in the finest clothes and gems the world has to offer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not enjoy that at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Marina...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.59,0:17:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness! The knight captain has urgent business to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What a boorish man, interrupting this gathering. Oh well, let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.49,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the emergency, Jenatos?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness. Your crown seems to have lost some of its luster.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.47,0:17:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:18:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It must feel good gazing down upon the world from your lofty throne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenatos?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.48,0:18:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ash has sullied the shine from your crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me clean it by taking your life!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.72,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.35,0:18:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Lower your sword at once, Jenatos!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'LL HACK AWAY THE ASH FROM THE CROWN!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,GUARDS! GUARDS!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,SEIZE HIM!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,LET ME GO! I HAVE TO CLEAR THE ASH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,OVERWHELM HIM AND TAKE HIM AWAY!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,UNHAND ME!!! I'M THE RIGHTFUL KING!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.49,0:18:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,REMEMBER, YOU'RE IN THE PALM OF GIZAFEAL'S HAND! HE'LL BE COMING FOR YOU NEXT!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.72,0:19:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hurt, your highness!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.92,0:19:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Jenatos!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, but he won't see the light of day again after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How dreadful. His wife even has a child on the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll grow up knowing they had a worthless father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that Gizafeal that Jenatos mentioned?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.94,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing. Just the vile rubbish of a man lost in his own darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.25,0:19:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing sulking in a place like this, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Does what happened with Jenatos still bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:20:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it... Say, Marina. What would you say my most precious thing in the world is?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly know that better than yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair. In that case, what's the most important thing to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.43,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have many things. You, my dear. My own life, perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it'll be our child when they're born. My parents are precious to me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.06,0:20:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. All things you can't purchase with wealth, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. You couldn't obtain any of those things with power alone, perhaps not even with wisdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Marina. I'm... thinking of traveling to Hermit's Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.41,0:20:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hermit's Island? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:21:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They say a skilled diviner lives there. I wish to seek his advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.49,0:21:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he should live inside that cave over there, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.89,0:21:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. I'll be heading there alone. You can return to the ship, minister.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.08,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright... Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Bats!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You wished to hear of your future self, did you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew I was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The holy mirror here always reflects what it needs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.76,0:22:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true you can read the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wish to find out? But please remember; the future may not hold the happiness you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All people will die one day. That won't phase me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I speak of the method of your death, not the death itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.80,0:22:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear nothing. Let me hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.01,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, give me your hand. ...oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.84,0:22:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You bear a burdensome ring. It would best be parted with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I... can't remove it. It's like it has become one with my flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what this ring is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.63,0:22:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I... I'm making too much of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.33,0:22:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, place your hands upon the mirror's pedestal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-Like this?\N-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.92,0:23:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the time spirits will bubble forth from the mirror's depths.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.94,0:23:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see treasure. The king and the queen. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A young child, just born.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they a boy? A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.03,0:23:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see yet. I see them crawling around. Ah, they're a healthy boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.13,0:23:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, a boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.49,0:23:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He grows up into a fine lad, no, a splendid man. ...oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.19,0:23:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.38,0:23:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.02,0:23:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. The mirror has clouded over.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:24:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened? What happens to me in the end!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.42,0:24:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...you would be better off not knowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.68,0:24:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I die of disease? In battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.75,0:24:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Much worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.33,0:24:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I grow tired of this! Just tell me already!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.20,0:24:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You fall to the ground... at the hands of your own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.78,0:24:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My son... kills me? Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.80,0:24:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.11,0:24:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This mirror must be spitting lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.12,0:24:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It is possible, I suppose. Though it has never lied before now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.36,0:24:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there no changing it? My destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.10,0:24:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I... do not know of such a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.01,0:24:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.86,0:25:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,With a heavy heart, the king returned to Heinrogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The terrible prophecy from the diviner repeated in his head over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.83,0:25:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You fall to the ground... at the hands of your own son.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.04,0:25:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What troubles you, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.60,0:25:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.73,0:25:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you learn anything from the diviner?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.09,0:25:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.58,0:25:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you heard, don't let it bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.80,0:25:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.14,0:25:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think he'll be back tonight, Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.58,0:25:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he will be. We received early word from a messenger about his imminent arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.16,0:25:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.03,0:25:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.58,0:26:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.01,0:26:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see... Oh, there it is! It really won't be much longer now!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.93,0:26:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so excited! Will it be a boy? Or a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.05,0:26:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait! I'm sure the king will be excited as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.37,0:26:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Definitely! Ahh, I don't want to wait any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.40,0:26:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The king has arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.56,0:26:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See, he's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.74,0:26:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia, what do you make of those two stars near the horizon?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.54,0:26:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I can't say I've seen those stars before.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.91,0:26:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they're twins nestling close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.73,0:26:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They are twin stars, after all, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.84,0:26:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Marina!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.33,0:26:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.02,0:26:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.15,0:26:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.85,0:26:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks and good work, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.44,0:27:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How were your travels?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.14,0:27:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Peaceful and uneventful, couldn't have been better.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.44,0:27:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful! So your task at Hermit's Island is finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.29,0:27:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? A-ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.40,0:27:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to hear all about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.18,0:27:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it really wasn't worth talking about. It was a waste of effort, going that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.35,0:27:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.40,0:27:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Marina?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.31,0:27:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.84,0:27:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness, the child inside of her kicked just a minute ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.15,0:27:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.79,0:27:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a very lively child. If it's a boy, he'll become a strong—
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.46,0:27:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I wish to sleep early tonight. Has the bed been prepared?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.39,0:27:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.82,0:27:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.86,0:28:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after, the queen gave birth to a healthy boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.36,0:28:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Announcing the crown prince!!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.99,0:28:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysteriously, another child was born at the same hour in a house close to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.82,0:28:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've brought dinner, my lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.96,0:28:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.25,0:28:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to eat something! We'll get you back to health soon to match the lively child you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:29:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhmm. At this rate, however, I'll have to miss out on the naming ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.50,0:29:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Oh, I heard an interesting rumor recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.83,0:29:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Another child was born at the same time as the crown prince. Any guesses as to whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.88,0:29:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.35,0:29:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Jenatos' child.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.68,0:29:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Jenatos'?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.04,0:29:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a girl they named Sarina.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.43,0:29:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sarina... It must be hard on the mother raising her alone after what her father did...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.19,0:29:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. It sounds like they're worried about how to raise Sarina alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.92,0:29:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd imagine...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.30,0:29:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the king might be convinced to pardon him?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.57,0:29:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not likely. Insurrection is a terrible crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.41,0:29:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.77,0:30:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia, would you mind opening the window? I'd love some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.47,0:30:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.32,0:30:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, fall has clearly arrived. Another week, and the leaves will start falling.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.18,0:30:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mhmm. Oh, those twin stars seem to have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.84,0:30:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were so bright even. It's almost as if the two stars themselves fell down and became your child and Sarina.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.37,0:30:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like that... It really does...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.78,0:30:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This child is meant to kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.37,0:30:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.06,0:31:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just twist his neck... he'd die right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.26,0:31:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If I simply drop him from this window...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.61,0:31:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...would my fate change?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.39,0:31:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there. Forgive me. This will all be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.76,0:31:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, king!? Stop it! Stop it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.01,0:31:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When did a pixie get here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.69,0:31:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Fara, remember it this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.35,0:31:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.16,0:31:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you doing with the child? You weren't going to throw him out the window, were you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.85,0:31:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,N-no...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.85,0:31:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on, but it's never okay to raise your hand against a defenseless child!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.88,0:32:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And isn't this your kid? You're not having an affair with your wife, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.54,0:32:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet you. How could you say that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.76,0:32:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Haha, sorry, sorry~ Let's just take a step back, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.28,0:32:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This child will one day—
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.28,0:32:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What a healthy boy! He'll be quite the rascal when he's older.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.27,0:32:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I come here for again... Oh right! I came here to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.74,0:32:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.56,0:32:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The forest we live in is gone now. The pixies and the elves have all left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.56,0:32:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Many went to neighboring countries, others underground. I'm about to leave myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.41,0:32:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be back?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.35,0:32:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows? But king, try not to make any more mistakes, okay? For both the country and yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.44,0:33:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, try to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.89,0:33:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.64,0:33:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Drawing water with a clean bucket leaves the well clean, but a filthy bucket will poison the well forever. Bye now!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.05,0:33:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.99,0:33:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.24,0:33:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.11,0:33:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The minister wishes to go over tomorrow's naming ceremony with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.99,0:33:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, got it...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.82,0:33:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww, aren't you glad your father held you up, you little prince~
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.24,0:33:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in quite the good mood, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.79,0:33:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He must love his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.71,0:33:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness, I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.73,0:33:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He really does look more and more like you by the day~ Maybe he'll grow larger and gaze down upon you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.85,0:33:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A-ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.24,0:34:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to the ceremony tomorrow, your highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.77,0:34:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of a name do you think the Six Gods will bestow upon him?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.46,0:34:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.39,0:34:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He was born under the dragon, so I'm sure the Dragon God's disciple will give him a fine name.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.77,0:34:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.51,0:34:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.36,0:34:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being dragged around left and right!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.82,0:34:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm being asked about seating for tomorrow, and now the guests are starting to quarrel with each other! I can't keep up!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.66,0:34:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, I'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.52,0:34:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, how does this sound for the seating of the visiting countries?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.46,0:34:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, no problems here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.46,0:34:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Next for the non-humans guests. I'm not sure why, but there's been no response from the elves or the pixies.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.74,0:34:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They refused the invitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.96,0:34:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No... They seem to have disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.68,0:35:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay it no mind. It's no great loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.56,0:35:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ceremony where the elves and pixies of the kingdom come here has meaning and—
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.44,0:35:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we invite who is not there?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.18,0:35:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,On another note, there are rumors of goblins and hobgoblins growing in numbers throughout the kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.96,0:35:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pick that topic up another time. Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.48,0:35:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The disciples of the Six Gods have accepted the invites.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.43,0:35:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That is to say, the Ocean God, the Mountain God, the Hero God, the Fertility Goddess, the Spirit God, and the Dragon God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.25,0:35:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.16,0:35:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With them here, I'm sure the naming ceremony will go smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.95,0:35:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.93,0:35:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing: as the royal family, you may decide if you wish to extend an invite to the Seventh God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.84,0:35:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventh God?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.73,0:35:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who rules the Underworld, Gizafeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.07,0:36:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, your highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.97,0:36:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Gizafeal is the one who rules over death?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.04,0:36:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.15,0:36:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... There's no need to invite someone like that to the naming ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.10,0:36:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.03,0:36:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any of my ancestors ever invited him in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.92,0:36:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing I've seen in our records going back several hundred years, but in older times—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.17,0:36:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.26,0:36:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gizafeal, while ruling over the dead, also rules over pleasure and fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.25,0:36:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand! How can he rule such opposites!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.12,0:36:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been told that those blessed by him with fortune and pleasure must pay the price while they're still of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.35,0:36:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What...!?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.16,0:37:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the leader of the goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.28,0:37:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.13,0:37:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm King Lewis.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.79,0:37:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg for your forgiveness, your highness! What brings you to this place where the sun doesn't shine?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.17,0:37:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I request a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.70,0:37:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd do anything for a king! Just, there's always—
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.86,0:37:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A price, I know. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.77,0:37:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's not enough, I'll bring more.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.77,0:37:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You must have something mighty important you need done! Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.66,0:37:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to you kidnap a baby... and kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.64,0:37:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.21,0:38:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador of the Hero God!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.20,0:38:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador of the Spirit God!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.27,0:38:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador of the Dragon God!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.67,0:38:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador of the Ocean God!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.32,0:38:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All the God's disciples seem to be arriving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.92,0:38:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You could be seeing the ceremony in person, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.85,0:38:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.74,0:38:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, my lady!?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.85,0:38:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Julia... Do you think I'll be able to see my child's first birthday...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.54,0:38:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying? Of course you will! You'll see him grow into a fine adult and even more beyond that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.56,0:38:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I... would love that...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.34,0:39:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right about now, the ambassadors should be presenting their gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.13,0:39:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,May the prince grow into a man beautiful in both body and heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.13,0:39:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,May the prince grow into a valiant hero who won't give up in the face of any hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.11,0:39:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,May the prince grow into a wise man with both deep knowledge and insight.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.81,0:39:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.27,0:39:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What, did you forget to invite me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.74,0:39:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.92,0:39:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only did you fail to invite me, but you thought you could receive my kindness without paying the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.04,0:40:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.69,0:40:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't lay a finger on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.86,0:40:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. I'm not here for the child. I'm here to collect on the king's debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.73,0:40:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,W-what do you mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.37,0:40:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play me for a fool! What was mine still resides on your finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.75,0:40:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this true, your highness!?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.37,0:40:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You underestimated me, boy. You made a promise, so now I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.22,0:40:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,For the sin of trying to dishonor Gizafeal, this country will once again fall into misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.19,0:40:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.14,0:40:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,AHH! AHHH!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.94,0:40:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, I will claim your most precious possession.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.04,0:40:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I've watched you closely to the very end, but I've decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.31,0:41:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking "you" yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.60,0:41:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,HELP ME!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,YOUR HIGHNESS!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.73,0:41:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,HELP ME!!! AHHH!!!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.45,0:41:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,HAHAHAHA!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.95,0:41:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall be mine for all eternity!!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.46,0:41:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-ABOVE! ABOVE! PROTECT HIS HIGHNESS AT ALL COSTS!!!\N-YES, SIR!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.94,0:41:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Minister, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.46,0:41:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.74,0:41:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What has fallen into Gizafeal's hands is forever lost. But, we still have the gift from my protector, the Dragon God.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.67,0:41:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.48,0:41:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll weaken Gizafeal's curse, if just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.96,0:41:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The prince will grow up and become the dawn upon this kingdom fallen to twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.01,0:42:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here and now, the Dragon God bestows upon the prince the name "Kai."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.80,0:42:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The king...!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.02,0:42:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're searching the castle for him now!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.90,0:42:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How could this be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.46,0:42:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But, at least the prince is safe and was given the name Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.96,0:42:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.45,0:42:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, he's even got a pendant from the Dragon God as proof of the naming ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.94,0:42:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.23,0:42:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.06,0:42:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There, that's the child! Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.03,0:42:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.44,0:42:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,OUTTA THE WAY!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.44,0:43:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Julia!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.28,0:43:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,HURRY IT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.52,0:43:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! What are you doing with him!?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.01,0:43:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill him, of course! Hahaha!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.85,0:43:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop! Give Kai back to me! KAI!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.70,0:43:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Before long, the queen fell into despair after losing both her husband and child, and soon took her last breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.42,0:43:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the king and the prince have not been seen since.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.08,0:43:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to Gizafeal's curse, the country fell to waste. One by one, the people abandoned the castle as it fell to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.28,0:44:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, 17 years came and went.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.19,0:44:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'm off, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.77,0:44:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going off on a journey, Sarina?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.76,0:44:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm off to find my own happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.19,0:44:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, don't tell anyone about your father. Especially any noblemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.86,0:44:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, I know. I hate those stuffy people, so I don't plan on talking to any either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.21,0:44:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh look, those two twin stars are back on the dawn's horizon again!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.97,0:44:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Back again?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.65,0:44:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They appeared once before on the day you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.10,0:44:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. It must be a good sign then. Well, I'm off, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.90,0:44:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay safe, Sarina.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.36,0:44:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come back for sure, then we can live an easier life.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.83,0:45:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm~ Should I take a slow journey this year, or laze around the forest some more? I can't decide~
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.49,0:45:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I should see how the Pixian Forest is doing! Maybe not, I'm sure it's still in terrible shape... No, I should see it anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.27,0:45:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kai? Are we going to be stuck here mining until the day we die?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.16,0:46:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lose hope, Michelia! I'm sure one day, we'll have our freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.22,0:46:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How far away will that day be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.60,0:46:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've actually been thinking of how to get away. I'll make sure we all escape from this slave camp, Michelia.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.27,0:46:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.03,0:46:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. And, I really want to know about my parents and homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.41,0:46:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai, look! Something's glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.73,0:46:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.42,0:46:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anything like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.96,0:46:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It gives me the creeps... We should throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.52,0:46:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not. This feels like it could be the harbinger for what's to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.97,0:47:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The curtain falls on one story, just as it rises on a new tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.28,0:47:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A tale of young warriors on a boundless adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.11,0:47:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A new page now turns in the story of Ancient Roman.
